---
import ArrowIcon from "./icons/ArrowIcon.astro"
---


<section class="pt-30" id="hero">
        <div class="max-w-6xl min-h-[75dvh] mx-auto px-3 items-center flex flex-col">
                <p class="py-1.5 mb-4  px-3 rounded-full  text-blue-600/90 inline-block font-bold border border-blue-600/30 shadow-2xl shadow-white/10 bg-blue-400/5  "> 
                    ● Oferta lanzamiento: 40% OFF primeros 5 clientes
                </p>

                <h1 class="tracking-tight text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl max-w-4xl font-bold text-center leading-tight">
                    Sitios web ultrarrápidos 
                    <span class="text-gray-400 font-semibold block">
                        sin complicaciones
                    </span>
                </h1>

                <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-center text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                    Landing pages y rediseños con tecnologia moderna. <span class="text-black font-bold">Velocidad garantizada menor a 2 segundos.</span> Sin costos de mantenimiento.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-9 flex gap-x-8 font-semibold">
                    <a href="#services" aria-label="Ir a la seccion de Contacto" class="bg-blue-700 text-white px-7 flex gap-x-2  py-4 border border-blue-700/30 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700/90   transition-all duration-200">
                        Ver Servicios
                        <div></div>
                        <ArrowIcon class="inline-block " >/
                    </a>

                    <a href="" aria-label="Ir a la seccion de servicios" class="border border-black/20 px-7 py-4 rounded-lg hover:border-black/30 hover:bg-black/5  transition-all duration-200 ">
                        Ver servicios
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 border-t border-gray-700 mx-auto mt-20 ">

                </div>

        </div>
</section>